snippet.title: Shadow Tactics: Aiko´s Choice - Release Date Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10009142

Aiko's Choice is a standalone expansion to the beloved stealth tactics game Shadow Tactics: Blades of the Shogun, set in Japan around the Edo period. 

Shadow Tactics: Aiko´s Choice launches on PlayStation 5 December 6, 2024. 
Pre-order now!
